name: Added GUI for 1.8-1.12
body: The artifact name for 1.8 to 1.12 changed to simpleclans-mc1.8

name: Fixed clan command
body:
Fixed clan command not working on older Minecraft versions
Added messages for join/leave/mute/unmute chat #603
Fixed clan tag min length #608
Added a check for too long colored tag #598

name: v2.10.3
body:
Fixed rank command and added new languages
Fixed globalff usage
Fixed Russian translation for the ff commands ("allow", "block" and
"auto")

name: v2.10.2
body:
Now saving periodically to db
Added update checker

name: v2.9.1
body:
SQLite queries use threads if enabled
Fixed last seen not updating
Fixed weird space in Menu command
Fixed Menu command messages getting cropped
Fixed Mojang URL
Added Metrics

name: v2.8.3
body:
Allow server owners to edit the time to collect member fee and upkeep
Added permission for using colors/formats on setrank
Fixed /clan home
Removed kdr-exempt from anyone.*

name: v2.8.0
body:
Added two ways to prevent players from grinding KDR. #276
When a player joins a clan, they automatically receive the
"group.tagname permission". #541 
Created a full PT-BR language file

name: v2.7.23
body:
Rejoin, clan list and member fee improved

- Cooldown on rejoining clans added. Closes #280
- You can now sort the clan list by name, size, etc. Closes #530
- Added a permission to bypass the member fee. Closes #540

KNOWN ISSUE:
The plugin will fail to load the data because the resign_times column is null by default.
To fix it, run this SQL query on your database: `UPDATE sc_players SET resign_times = "{}";`

name: v2.7.22
body:
Clan descriptions implemented
Clans that don't have the member fee enabled can bypass the upkeep charge

name: v2.7.19
body:
Purge command, percentage to demote & bb on purge

Command to purge a player was added, it can be used by the console or by an admin
Menu command edited to show the new command and the demote command for admins
When a player is purged, a message is added to the clan bb
The plugin now considers the percentage (set in the config) of online leaders to demote another player

name: v2.7.17
body:
Implemented a member fee as suggested on #254 
Improved the resign command

name: v2.7.16
body: Bulletin Board improved as described in #487

name: v2.7.15
body:
Admins can demote clan leaders
Permission added: "simpleclans.admin.demote"
3 new messages added as well
Resign command now asks for confirmation

name: v2.7.14
body:
Fixed clan and ally chats using the same format
Also removed unnecessary usage of replaceAll
